{
  "stem": "15115.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When they started the transportation, which is in early January, I think, according to my book here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took the people from Baron Hirsch so they didn't have to move them, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So then they start taking the different types, parts, of Salonika into Singrou.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They made another ghetto, Singrou.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was a high class Jewish people there at this section.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They moved the people-- they started-- the Greeks were moving out and they were putting more Jews in there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So then they started taking us down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We, or where I used to live, because, I used to live in a section what I would say 50-50, it was not all Jews.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Just there in the apartment where we used to live, it was only three Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Three Jewish families and seven Gentile families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a story building, five-- then apartments, five on each side, see?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were at the bottom, first floor bottom one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In the building of the then apartments there were only three Jewish families and the rest were all Gentile families.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Actually, from where I used to live, I will say it was more Gentile than Jewish people, you know, living there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So it came to our time that we had to evacuate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So they put us into Singrou.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "When it came time to packing to go into Singrou--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Whatever was left over, which was not much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything which-- I sold already most of the stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The good expensive stuff I sold.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had a wagon so we could put the stuff, and they gave us an apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or they gave us one room, I guess, for the whole family or something like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I remember correct.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
